::DarkMouse::
She turned at the sound of Scorponpok's voice.
"HEY! Glad to see that you madeit back in one piece.  I'm going to show 
Quickstrike the tunnel I made today.  You can join if you want?"
She saw Scorponok walk off to his lab.
"Or you can go and do....that." Her voice kind of trail off.
She looked at Quickstrike and gave a friendly smile.
"Well commander.  I'll let you inspect my work and you can tell me how you 
like it."
She continued down to the tunnel.
